Option Explicit 

Sub FemtoMeasure( VAL, probe )

     Dim dummy 
     
     Select Case ( probe ) 
     '
          Case 1
               VAL = FEMTO.Measure( CStr("1000000001"), CStr("1000000001"), dummy, dummy, dummy, dummy, dummy )
          Case 2
               VAL = FEMTO.Measure( CStr("1000000002"), CStr("1000000002"), dummy, dummy, dummy, dummy, dummy )
          Case 3
               VAL = FEMTO.Measure( CStr("1000000003"), CStr("1000000003"), dummy, dummy, dummy, dummy, dummy )
          Case 4
               VAL = FEMTO.Measure( CStr("1000000004"), CStr("1000000004"), dummy, dummy, dummy, dummy, dummy )
          Case Else 
               MsgBox "Fatal Error: FemtoMeasure()"
               Exit Sub  
     '
     End Select 

End Sub
